<subSubSection pageId="38" pageNumber="39" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,1057,1670]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
REMARKS: The “Corrigenda” in 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[557,798,1292,1318]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" refId="ref145440" refString="Rondani, C. (1861 e) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol. IV. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analatica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars tertia: Muscidae, Tachininarum complementum. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma]. 174 pp. [31 December +] [For dating, see Sabrosky (1961) and Evenhuis (1997: 662).]" type="book" year="1861">Rondani (1861e: 8)</bibRefCitation>
indicated that the genus-group name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1856" box="[1276,1435,1292,1317]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Bombylisoma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[1276,1435,1292,1317]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bombylisoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be changed to 
<taxonomicName authority="Loew, 1855" authorityName="Loew" authorityYear="1855" box="[526,810,1331,1357]" class="Insecta" family="Bombyliidae" genus="Dischistus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[526,648,1331,1356]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Dischistus</emphasis>
Loew, 1855
</taxonomicName>
, but this was an act of synonymy and not a new replacement name. 
<bibRefCitation author="Marschall, A. F. de" box="[480,745,1370,1396]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" refId="ref137580" refString="Marschall, A. F. de (1873) Nomenclator zoologicus continens nomina systematica generum animalium tam viventium quam fossilium, secundum ordinem alphabeticum disposita. C. Ueberreuter, Vindobonae [= Vienna]. v + 482 pp. [5 November] [Date presented to the Zoologisch-Botanischen Gesellschaft in Wien.]" type="book" year="1873">Marschall (1873: 323)</bibRefCitation>
listed the spelling 
<emphasis box="[975,1141,1370,1395]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bombylosoma</emphasis>
and this was cited as an unjustified emendation by 
<bibRefCitation author="Zaitzev, A. I." box="[574,817,1410,1436]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="43 - 169" refId="ref154146" refString="Zaitzev, A. I. (1989 a) Family Bombyliidae, pp. 43 - 169. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 6. Therevidae - Empididae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest. 435 pp. [1 March] [Dated from Evenhuis (2008 b).]" type="book chapter" year="1989">Zaitzev (1989a: 84)</bibRefCitation>
, but criteria for making this name available as an emendation were not found to be fulfilled in 
<bibRefCitation author="Marschall, A. F. de" box="[788,996,1449,1475]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" refId="ref137580" refString="Marschall, A. F. de (1873) Nomenclator zoologicus continens nomina systematica generum animalium tam viventium quam fossilium, secundum ordinem alphabeticum disposita. C. Ueberreuter, Vindobonae [= Vienna]. v + 482 pp. [5 November] [Date presented to the Zoologisch-Botanischen Gesellschaft in Wien.]" type="book" year="1873">Marschall (1873)</bibRefCitation>
. Similarly, 
<bibRefCitation author="Zaitzev, A. I." box="[1135,1369,1449,1475]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="43 - 169" refId="ref154146" refString="Zaitzev, A. I. (1989 a) Family Bombyliidae, pp. 43 - 169. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 6. Therevidae - Empididae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest. 435 pp. [1 March] [Dated from Evenhuis (2008 b).]" type="book chapter" year="1989">Zaitzev (1989a: 84)</bibRefCitation>
cited the spelling 
<emphasis box="[390,564,1488,1513]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bombyliosoma</emphasis>
of Verrall 
<emphasis box="[693,716,1488,1513]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">in</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Scudder, S. H." box="[724,949,1488,1514]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="1 - 376" refId="ref149640" refString="Scudder, S. H. (1882) Nomenclator zoologicus. An alphabetical list of all generic names that have been employed by naturalists for recent and fossil animals from the earliest times to the close of the year 1879. I. Supplemental list of genera in zoology. List of generic names employed in zoology and paleontology to the close of the year 1879, chiefly supplemental to those catalogued by Agassiz and Marschall, or indexed in the Zoological Record. Bulletin of the United States National Museum, 19 [i], i - xxi, 1 - 376. [August] [Recorded in the August issue of American Journal of Science.]" type="journal article" year="1882">Scudder (1882: 47)</bibRefCitation>
as an unjustified emendation, but criteria for making this name available as an emendation were not found to be fulfilled in 
<bibRefCitation author="Scudder, S. H." box="[1245,1432,1527,1553]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" pagination="1 - 376" refId="ref149640" refString="Scudder, S. H. (1882) Nomenclator zoologicus. An alphabetical list of all generic names that have been employed by naturalists for recent and fossil animals from the earliest times to the close of the year 1879. I. Supplemental list of genera in zoology. List of generic names employed in zoology and paleontology to the close of the year 1879, chiefly supplemental to those catalogued by Agassiz and Marschall, or indexed in the Zoological Record. Bulletin of the United States National Museum, 19 [i], i - xxi, 1 - 376. [August] [Recorded in the August issue of American Journal of Science.]" type="journal article" year="1882">Scudder (1882)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<emphasis box="[247,413,1566,1591]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bombylosoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Marschall, A. F. de" box="[424,618,1566,1592]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39" refId="ref137580" refString="Marschall, A. F. de (1873) Nomenclator zoologicus continens nomina systematica generum animalium tam viventium quam fossilium, secundum ordinem alphabeticum disposita. C. Ueberreuter, Vindobonae [= Vienna]. v + 482 pp. [5 November] [Date presented to the Zoologisch-Botanischen Gesellschaft in Wien.]" type="book" year="1873">Marschall, 1873</bibRefCitation>
and 
<emphasis box="[683,857,1566,1591]" italics="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bombyliosoma</emphasis>
Verrall, 1882 are thus unavailable names, 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">new status</emphasis>
.
</paragraph>
